    "created_at": "2017-02-14T17:35:34Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-02-14T17:51:59Z",
    "body": "Closing this out, @danyaal please feel free to open any new pull requests to improve the documentation in this area for things that are unclear or vague, but node integration definitely needs to be enabled on a window for a `<webview>` tag to be added to it. The `<webview>` tag can have node disabled though if it is loading remote or untrusted content."
